Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不起床的话要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该决定志愿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱的事情不用担心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君做想做的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 吃相太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天会晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭你自己先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就是最后的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何别留下遗憾好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的暑假吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【歌词】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:40.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻先で揺れる残り香消すように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:47.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,足早に過ぎてゆく夏の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:56.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,制服のボタンも少しだけこすれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:03.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,通りのベンチさえも時を刻んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:11.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの夏は今も僕らを待っているかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:21.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,振り返る君の笑顔 焼き付けたフィルムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れない…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:28.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束も 駆け抜ける潮騒も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:36.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,花火が写した仲間と笑う一瞬さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:43.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,薄れない愛しさも 遠くなる思い出も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかで待ってる季節へのエンドロール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:52.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,シャッターを開いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れない…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:13.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束も 駆け抜ける潮騒も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:21.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,花火が写した仲間と笑う一瞬さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:28.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,バラバラの僕たちの思い出も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:33.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかで待ってる未来へjoint-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:39.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,フィルムを繋いで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:40.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,像是鼻尖飘过的一丝香气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:47.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的风快步地吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:56.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,校服上的纽扣 也擦到了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:03.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,路边的长椅 也留下了时光的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:11.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天 如今仍然在等待我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:21.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,你回眸一笑的情景 已然印在胶片中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会忘记…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:28.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的约定 汹涌的海潮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:36.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,以烟花为背景与伙伴们一起欢笑的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:43.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,永不褪色的喜爱 日渐遥远的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,是通向那个等待着我们的季节的end-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:52.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,打开快门…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会忘记…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:13.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的约定 汹涌的海潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:21.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,以烟花为背景与伙伴们一起欢笑的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:28.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每个人的回忆片段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:33.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,是通向未来的joint-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:39.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,用手上的胶片接起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…欲求不满么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给应该在宝贵的暑假期间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力学习的海人君带来慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过散漫得似乎完全不需要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息啦 休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 杀必死时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪来的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 今天什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜让我来看看阿海你有没有好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊 没一点信任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就别偷懒好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不懂就跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么可让你教的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家里做的话 老姐会嫌很难闻什么的诸多意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈美姐又回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经是病了 治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿聪这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她老公很忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说外星人相关是顶级机密什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么问也不透露一点口风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说今天柑菜会去她家住下一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生之间的秘密会议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容的话多少能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢骚啦 牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎的包里有情书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有三封
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下之前先给我拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎爱装酷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来呢后来呢 情书怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是当场撕掉扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太 太狠了吧美樱同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不狠一点 阿哲是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哲一直都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是考虑对方的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不表达自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 美樱 唔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看美樱 烤炉预热好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}虽然我也知道他很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}但总该有好好摆明自己态度的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一个月前被他姐姐叫出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北原的心情我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你没对大家说你们在交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那个怎么说来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点小难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说啥啊 该做的事都做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别弄太乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是阿海说了奇怪的话吧 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了什么奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有自觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁才是猥琐大叔啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 坐垫下面找到了这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胶片卷盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来之前整理过胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候的胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是拍电影之前试拍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 哲郎个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是公开好好说明啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让美樱那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去死 先杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 都说了那封信不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像跟偶像信差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万人迷就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说喜欢我就不生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:09:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超 超爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服的澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也是说过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿哲的心意我是知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}今天去过雾岛君家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像不闹情绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了8毫米的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雾岛君家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8毫米是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在那里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍电影之前说试拍什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聚在阿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上玩烟花的时候拍过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过怎么又翻出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是整理胶片的时候拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后忘记收回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 现在还…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.69,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,294)}我们在高中最后的夏天 等待着那个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐明天要早起就先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了很怀念的胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天不叫你起床了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 已经在拍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么在意就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的啦 贵月学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是测试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会用在正片里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也放松不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿海 反光板像这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 石垣君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 你在搞什么攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 只要慢慢走过来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出点环顾周围景色的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右手和右脚一起出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这电影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这次就改下曝光度再拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从原来的地方重新来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜 刚才为止拍了多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多正好一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3分钟还挺长的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说阿海 这样真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市花学姐的演技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话就是连外行都不如
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是第一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几天后就要开始拍摄了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持自然真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都紧张得口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜的真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再来一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么神出鬼没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 剧本完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了写出更完美的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算好好观察扮演女主角的市花以激发灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没写好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看着市花学姐那演技也想不出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好妩媚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差2岁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么有这么大差别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿海 摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要拍吗 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体发热了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人有点奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}等下美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛 眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}眼镜压到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}话说前面都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 拍摄到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？为 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为什么 就是不拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气呢 谷川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么 又不是在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 都是因为学姐有点不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 变得很奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川同学 害羞的表情被拍到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 灵感像开水一样涌出来根本停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能看啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在这里睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像安稳地睡了 现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉态度突然就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是不习惯拍摄累着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是拍了一点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子还能拍什么电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 市花是个说做就一定做到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾岛君你能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试复习的时候深刻体会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你跟贵月学姐发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么 两人一起学习到半夜而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样被学姐教了很多事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有像恋爱故事那样在浴室来个心跳情景什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么啊 阿海和学姐两人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了一个月都没有发生什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说还是说说电影的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得大家都在场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就一声不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都不像没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 好了 回到原来的话题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 要说回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没跟贵月学生发生什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回到那么前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想蒙混过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别缠人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}什么都没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样……才叫缠人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弃权 弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川 我弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸 胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…也碰到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵 大家都好棒 呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我买来了好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎么了 大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花买过来了 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺有劲头的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 给我火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哲烧完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我来拿下个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海君 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出来什么内容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好 接下来两个一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 北原 谷川 柠檬学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有市花学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也拍到谷川的肚脐眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上给我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 我也要玩更好看的 来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是能拿在手上的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}来 拿这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}好啦 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是要去东京的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来还想再拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让人叫好的happy end的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们成长的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好 剩下来的也大玩一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棱角都慢慢变得模糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人焦躁 让人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:23:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次看到留下的胶片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 如果没有遇到学姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定活得跟现在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这不是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在继续着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.72,0:24:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映在胶片上的……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天的……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.21,0:25:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结尾字幕
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【歌词】
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:22.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,消えた 花火の後は
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:30.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,苦い火薬の香り
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,燻る視界の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.87,0:25:44.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ高さの君の視線を見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ふたり同時に はにかんだりしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.46,0:26:03.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らはただがむしゃらに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.93,0:26:11.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用な言葉で 未来を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.45,0:26:16.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,迫りくる衝動を抱え込む
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:25.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもなく幸せな結末を望んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:32.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,眩しい あの夏の日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:22.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,熄灭的烟花 留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:30.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,是有点苦的火药香味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,烟熏的视界前方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.87,0:25:44.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到了你在同一水平的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:59.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,结果你我双方 同时害羞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.46,0:26:03.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一心忘我地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.93,0:26:11.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,以不成熟的言语 去探寻未来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.45,0:26:16.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,拥抱汹涌而至的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:25.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望一个完美的幸福结局
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:32.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天的时光 是如此的耀眼
